---
title: Jerk Veggie Burgers with Beyond Meat® and Mango Salsa
description: Take a trip to the Caribbean with Jamaican-inspired Beyond Meat® burgers. Toasted artisan buns are filled with jerk-spiced veggie patties and a slather of lime mayo. A fresh mango salsa cuts through the spice and brings some sweet to the heat.
